彻底销毁、无法还原，当地还邀请了第三方审计和公证处参与工作。至此，无锡市第一批涉疫个人数据实现成功销毁，全力保障了公民个人数据安全。 同时，门铃码、疫查通、货运通行证等「数字防疫」40 多项应用，也于当天功成身退，陆续下线。 据了解，无锡市「数字防疫」服务上线以来，共搜集了 10 亿条个人数据，主要用于核酸筛查、流调溯源、外防输入性疫情、重点人群核酸检测等用途。公证处公证，销毁仪式举行！10 亿条个人信息被彻底销毁，服务下线！事关每个人，广东此前也做过"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-bfc12ec1839498813b79e8a679942c2e_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "40 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/587278658"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI+rSWp/T0sIAfEAMaCDkyNzg3OTk5ILWnhaAGMBM4ugFAD3IJNTg3Mjc4NjU4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1677946212.8829367", "card_id": "Q_553849188", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1244}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "年轻人宁买万元手机不愿花 4 元充电，背后的消费心理是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "iPhone14 全面发售后，诸如充电宝、手机壳等周边设备也是被一路带火。尤其是在近一段时间，共享充电宝不断涨价，让无数年轻人直呼「充电刺客」，也间接使得磁吸充电宝在近半年的网上销售额同比去年猛增超 100%。 年轻人宁买万元手机不花 4 元充电 直呼「充电刺客」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-8ed8d4d71652df6a2523d64757af341d_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "36 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/553849188"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI+rSWp/T0sIAfEAMaCDg1MzYwODM4II+xj5kGMFk45AxAEHIJNTUzODQ5MTg4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1677946212.8845673", "card_id": "Q_417457238", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 96}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你认为，溺爱孩子和关爱孩子真正的区别在哪里？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-ed96d2f5193706d6b5d9ec1fe85358cd_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "30 万热度", "font_color": ""